msgid "Built with Rust and Slint, and powered by Rodio and Symphonia. With thanks to Qobuz, MusicBrainz, Song.link/Odesli, LRCLIB, lyrics.ovh, and Lucide."
msgstr "Gebouwd met Rust en Slint, en aangedreven door Rodio en Symphonia. Met dank aan Qobuz, MusicBrainz, Song.link/Odesli, LRCLIB, lyrics.ovh en Lucide."

