msgid "JACK is not bit-perfect"
msgstr "JACK is niet bit-perfect"

msgid "The JACK backend routes audio through the JACK graph, which resamples to the graph's sample rate. For bit-perfect playback use ALSA (direct) or PipeWire with passthrough."
msgstr "De JACK-backend routeert audio door de JACK-graaf, die resamplet naar de samplefrequentie van de graaf. Gebruik voor bit-perfecte weergave ALSA (direct) of PipeWire met passthrough."

